    ('Zambia Grid Diversification PPA Programme', 'Zambia', 'Southern Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Zambia signed a record number of Power Purchase Agreements (PPAs) as part of efforts to diversify its heavily hydro-dependent electricity grid. The ERB and energy authorities are driving the procurement to reduce vulnerability to drought-related power shortages. The PPAs mark a significant shift toward a more balanced renewable energy mix in Zambia.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2026, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMitAFBVV95cUxNeVhHbmdHeXJmRnBPY2RZYW1vWG1KUkEtNTBRNzFYeU9DN3dsOVZZNUVTT0JlTUo5Y2U0eHozZDJtS0xUSlpuSWljNlNBLVlyRDBCZllvQ2pzNlBzS2JIZ3p3YjUxX0hNNGY1OUZyMlZSYmlNMDRyWFpTN1FzbkRXVTk4Z3RlS0NsWmF1VUlzMTBiTDhYNFhVc0ZNWDZ6MlVlVjFGeVh1RjY2OFJrQ1IzSm1aSFo?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMitAFBVV95cUxNeVhHbmdHeXJmRnBPY2RZYW1vWG1KUkEtNTBRNzFYeU9DN3dsOVZZNUVTT0JlTUo5Y2U0eHozZDJtS0xUSlpuSWljNlNBLVlyRDBCZllvQ2pzNlBzS2JIZ3p3YjUxX0hNNGY1OUZyMlZSYmlNMDRyWFpTN1FzbkRXVTk4Z3RlS0NsWmF1VUlzMTBiTDhYNFhVc0ZNWDZ6MlVlVjFGeVh1RjY2OFJrQ1IzSm1aSFo?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Garneton North Solar Project', 'Zambia', 'Southern Africa', 'Solar', 14.54, 'African Development Bank (AfDB)', 'financing closed', 'The African Development Bank Group approved a $14.54 million investment to support the Garneton North Solar Project in Zambia. The project is part of Zambia''s broader renewable energy drive to diversify its power generation mix away from hydropower. The AfDB''s funding is intended to accelerate the development of utility-scale solar capacity in the country.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.?oc=5', 'https://news.google.?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Zambia Sugar Power Generation Expansion (100 MW)', 'Zambia', 'Southern Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Zambia Sugar announced plans to expand its on-site power generation capacity to 100 MW, likely through bagasse-based or solar cogeneration. The expansion would significantly increase the company''s self-generation capability and could contribute surplus power to the national grid. The announcement reflects a growing trend of agro-industrial companies investing in captive power in Zambia.', NULL, NULL, 100, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiowFBVV95cUxQOVI2X21RT2pFUVhXQ09HVmI5N3QzNlpaV0ZUQUVoXzBmQlNjTTdQOWJ3bDBhaVZFTTZFcURTdWNlb0plZlJVQjFtcjUwOExlZWxRcE5XS2pocTlVTkEzV0FuTzZlTUljbThPOVRzeHRvUVlnUF80M2h6Y1k1SThOeWFPLWNEc3RGLW1WUmF6R3ZmM3BtYmllYTM2ZFR0Nl85MVpB?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiowFBVV95cUxQOVI2X21RT2pFUVhXQ09HVmI5N3QzNlpaV0ZUQUVoXzBmQlNjTTdQOWJ3bDBhaVZFTTZFcURTdWNlb0plZlJVQjFtcjUwOExlZWxRcE5XS2pocTlVTkEzV0FuTzZlTUljbThPOVRzeHRvUVlnUF80M2h6Y1k1SThOeWFPLWNEc3RGLW1WUmF6R3ZmM3BtYmllYTM2ZFR0Nl85MVpB?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Uganda Co-located Battery Energy Storage System (250 MWh)', 'Uganda', 'East Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'Energy America', 'announced', 'Uganda''s Electricity Regulatory Authority approved a 250 MWh co-located battery energy storage system (BESS) project led by a subsidiary of Energy America. The project will be co-located with a generation facility to enhance grid stability and reliability. The approval marks a significant step in Uganda''s integration of large-scale storage into its power system.', NULL, NULL, 250, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwAFBVV95cUxOMXUzRm5uNU1ScXVSSTFqT0pNQVp5akFEZjNDZ3FwbmIzbTBiTlktQXFzLUJ3Ti05WUlseUFCdFgxVGNWZkczRE9reGlzc0hRcmh4XzFZdFZHcXdIMXd5OVlrZi0zcUlpc2t6V3F5QjNFcTBQb2lKZmcxOEhKSGZRS2Nlalp0WVdxUUVyLWpwOENsclcxcTg2WjJHWGhneldsNGpPT3MwalRObmRhTV9sckU2OGJ1VUEyWko3OHdNWG8?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwAFBVV95cUxOMXUzRm5uNU1ScXVSSTFqT0pNQVp5akFEZjNDZ3FwbmIzbTBiTlktQXFzLUJ3Ti05WUlseUFCdFgxVGNWZkczRE9reGlzc0hRcmh4XzFZdFZHcXdIMXd5OVlrZi0zcUlpc2t6V3F5QjNFcTBQb2lKZmcxOEhKSGZRS2Nlalp0WVdxUUVyLWpwOENsclcxcTg2WjJHWGhneldsNGpPT3MwalRObmRhTV9sckU2OGJ1VUEyWko3OHdNWG8?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Uganda 100 MW Solar and Battery Storage Project', 'Uganda', 'East Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Uganda''s energy regulatory authority approved a 100 MW solar project integrated with battery storage, marking a major step in the country''s clean energy expansion. The project will combine solar photovoltaic generation with storage to provide dispatchable renewable power. The approval signals growing regulatory support for hybrid renewable energy systems in Uganda.', NULL, NULL, 100, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMikgFBVV95cUxPODY2Ym1QU25aUDBVMmhmU19kbmhSZU5LT3h2LVhDZkMtcDRtRzI5YmpNWjZmY1UxdGVhd05MUmtreGx6ZXAtNDFmTFhvOU56bXpHU2dpZDROU0tIbUp2MWNvUXprQVFPS0dGZlQzR0xHRC15QldZUjR5UjRIZnQwMEowWEpaLTZYVTZhWTcwRm1pUQ?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMikgFBVV95cUxPODY2Ym1QU25aUDBVMmhmU19kbmhSZU5LT3h2LVhDZkMtcDRtRzI5YmpNWjZmY1UxdGVhd05MUmtreGx6ZXAtNDFmTFhvOU56bXpHU2dpZDROU0tIbUp2MWNvUXprQVFPS0dGZlQzR0xHRC15QldZUjR5UjRIZnQwMEowWEpaLTZYVTZhWTcwRm1pUQ?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('AIIM ATAF Clean Energy and Infrastructure Fund', 'Tanzania', 'East Africa', 'Solar', 50, 'AIIM (African Infrastructure Investment Managers)', 'announced', 'AIIM (African Infrastructure Investment Managers) advanced a $50 million Africa Transition and Acceleration Fund (ATAF) to support clean energy and infrastructure projects across Africa. The fund is designed to catalyse investment in renewable energy and sustainable infrastructure on the continent. The initiative represents a significant commitment to accelerating Africa''s energy transition.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2026, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMixAFBVV95cUxOaDRuNFVKWWIxYWh6UHRvWmlqUndQRVBmTExNUkNtcW9rWEZOanAzRndmSTRWRmxEbGR0eFVXSlgxOUF6ajdUVWRZVjZMR0VNSndZbkJLelVNRUNFeW5Id1NraUE0SkRHZUEtZXpDY1RTblBIRThRYk9EWWdUdWZTYTZYWkwxY2FUVmRVWU03R2lKRVRjcXNFaVYxUEM5S04zZzV2eUdqNmpicmpNUzN0bmVRbDF2MmZkRkN2aGhVSGV1RWlQ?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMixAFBVV95cUxOaDRuNFVKWWIxYWh6UHRvWmlqUndQRVBmTExNUkNtcW9rWEZOanAzRndmSTRWRmxEbGR0eFVXSlgxOUF6ajdUVWRZVjZMR0VNSndZbkJLelVNRUNFeW5Id1NraUE0SkRHZUEtZXpDY1RTblBIRThRYk9EWWdUdWZTYTZYWkwxY2FUVmRVWU03R2lKRVRjcXNFaVYxUEM5S04zZzV2eUdqNmpicmpNUzN0bmVRbDF2MmZkRkN2aGhVSGV1RWlQ?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Amea Power Egypt 1 GW Solar-Plus-Storage Plant', 'Egypt', 'North Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'Amea Power', 'under construction', 'Amea Power has begun construction on a large-scale 1 GW solar plant combined with 600 MWh of battery storage in Egypt. The project represents one of the largest solar-plus-storage developments on the African continent. Its scale signals growing investor confidence in Egypt as a hub for utility-scale renewable energy.', NULL, NULL, 1000, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMirAFBVV95cUxPQlVnNWtPa05kaUhWbk53WHJpdktCTzZ6MHRYZ201M1lROHhFS29ScWthUVpPZFFxcEdLOUw0Z1ZmVWpEeDdiVkZwN2k0UXNwMUx1R3laMlFSNFoyeVNmYUY0SWdZSVRFRG5KTHlkSWhvX3N4cHlWU2RJNmJjZmJYMEM3aVgyTThtMzNUZGJWREh1OExGU2JKQW5tdWlPRXVfZ253Q0dQUzBVU3B4', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMirAFBVV95cUxPQlVnNWtPa05kaUhWbk53WHJpdktCTzZ6MHRYZ201M1lROHhFS29ScWthUVpPZFFxcEdLOUw0Z1ZmVWpEeDdiVkZwN2k0UXNwMUx1R3laMlFSNFoyeVNmYUY0SWdZSVRFRG5KTHlkSWhvX3N4cHlWU2RJNmJjZmJYMEM3aVgyTThtMzNUZGJWREh1OExGU2JKQW5tdWlPRXVfZ253Q0dQUzBVU3B4', true, 'approved', 'Construction', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('PriVida Power Mini-Grid Financing', 'Nigeria', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'financing closed', 'PriVida Power has secured funding to develop and expand mini-grid projects across Africa. The funding is aimed at catalysing clean energy access in underserved rural communities. Specific financial details and the lead investors have not been disclosed in the article summary.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMilAFBVV95cUxNNFJYTUdsWWxldHpZZzRTSGRuWDVpQkp0OURrUVFFakFQdXJJUFJmNUhHTFB2Z3pSNnpJQ1NUY3NWU1RTeDctdnRBWWtLUGdacmpSSXZ6RC1qNWx0TWd2T3VscHNUZ1NNMlpfN2lfOEtGMWdKNTFBenRKN000S041OVIwbGhQTTZpcWxWd2pSZC1DOEFD', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMilAFBVV95cUxNNFJYTUdsWWxldHpZZzRTSGRuWDVpQkp0OURrUVFFakFQdXJJUFJmNUhHTFB2Z3pSNnpJQ1NUY3NWU1RTeDctdnRBWWtLUGdacmpSSXZ6RC1qNWx0TWd2T3VscHNUZ1NNMlpfN2lfOEtGMWdKNTFBenRKN000S041OVIwbGhQTTZpcWxWd2pSZC1DOEFD', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Husk Power Solar Mini-Grids Nigeria', 'Nigeria', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'IFC, Canada (Government of Canada)', 'financing closed', 'The IFC and the Government of Canada have jointly invested in Husk Power Systems to catalyse solar-powered economic growth in rural Nigeria. The investment is intended to expand Husk''s portfolio of solar mini-grids serving off-grid and underserved communities. This deal underscores international development finance support for distributed renewable energy access in Sub-Saharan Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMivAFBVV95cUxNVUlWZkVhNldyZXNnbW95cDRTOVJya3VMaldSVUNJNjNDZ2lFQnZjb01TZU02VHRLcm9LUDRxQUgtYk1vYXRuaExLLXZ4RHFtRGFVNVYwT1FPRklSUDQtcFdDQTQ4ZGppVVB5cXlnblgxQ3FvZXFjSDV1TzBqbHFnNWdPWFpxWGYxZkotOGEtOTRwVm96ZUwzMlFyODh3dmJCeGpJRVIydlNydzlQY190WWFLXzRGN0wzYzJTRw', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMivAFBVV95cUxNVUlWZkVhNldyZXNnbW95cDRTOVJya3VMaldSVUNJNjNDZ2lFQnZjb01TZU02VHRLcm9LUDRxQUgtYk1vYXRuaExLLXZ4RHFtRGFVNVYwT1FPRklSUDQtcFdDQTQ4ZGppVVB5cXlnblgxQ3FvZXFjSDV1TzBqbHFnNWdPWFpxWGYxZkotOGEtOTRwVm96ZUwzMlFyODh3dmJCeGpJRVIydlNydzlQY190WWFLXzRGN0wzYzJTRw', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Nigeria AfDB Economic Governance and Energy Transition Loan', 'Nigeria', 'West Africa', 'Solar', 500, 'African Development Bank (AfDB)', 'financing closed', 'The African Development Bank Group approved a $500 million loan to Nigeria to support economic governance reforms and the country''s energy transition agenda. The financing is intended to accelerate structural reforms underpinning Nigeria''s shift to cleaner energy sources and improved energy sector management. This marks a significant development finance commitment to Nigeria''s energy transformation.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMi-', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMi-', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Wärtsilä 30 MW Power Plant Nigeria', 'Nigeria', 'West Africa', 'Oil & Gas', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Wärtsilä has been selected to supply equipment and solutions for a 30 MW power plant project in Nigeria. The project represents Wärtsilä''s continued expansion in the Nigerian power sector, providing flexible generation capacity. The plant is expected to help address Nigeria''s significant electricity supply deficit.', NULL, NULL, 30, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiswFBVV95cUxOeV84VU9lR1llRHpRRlhidWZ3blVXa0hYNlhnMUhGSG5oM293Q3JuRlotWDdKdm1MbjE3RTQ3MXlLOTBXQkxXRVc0TU5lRkFYX21EWm9Wa1JRYWhWNHBEeFU2YVN1dnRSVElGY3NSb0trTlBXUEU1elE1ZDVmMTVWUWtrSnZCajNFcFE0cTJlbk8tSTJSWGFiWXM4ZFltZVdpWGlST3BNTjNNZTlVN2hFNDhpOA', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiswFBVV95cUxOeV84VU9lR1llRHpRRlhidWZ3blVXa0hYNlhnMUhGSG5oM293Q3JuRlotWDdKdm1MbjE3RTQ3MXlLOTBXQkxXRVc0TU5lRkFYX21EWm9Wa1JRYWhWNHBEeFU2YVN1dnRSVElGY3NSb0trTlBXUEU1elE1ZDVmMTVWUWtrSnZCajNFcFE0cTJlbk8tSTJSWGFiWXM4ZFltZVdpWGlST3BNTjNNZTlVN2hFNDhpOA', true, 'approved', 'Announced', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('South Africa Battery Storage Procurement Round', 'South Africa', 'Southern Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'tender', 'South Africa''s battery storage procurement process attracted 33 bids, indicating strong investor interest in grid-scale energy storage in the country. The procurement is part of South Africa''s broader effort to stabilize its electricity grid and integrate more renewable energy. The high number of bids reflects growing competition in the African battery storage market.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2024, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMilAFBVV95cUxOTm83R0VDWW1jRHBQVWFHTFBsYXlnTHI0TmlQQjNhMTFsOGVpQVd3NW94blhZZnpjMmowdU55ZU95SGZRWXBEOUo0dUN0eEFLeVNWRVRNNE1CRWI0R29DZnhTSHJ6X09tNDQ1Q2pkM2lJMEsxbXN6LW5WbjBOWnBXU2hmc3YzNG5rdDNaLTcwbXlrekM2', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMilAFBVV95cUxOTm83R0VDWW1jRHBQVWFHTFBsYXlnTHI0TmlQQjNhMTFsOGVpQVd3NW94blhZZnpjMmowdU55ZU95SGZRWXBEOUo0dUN0eEFLeVNWRVRNNE1CRWI0R29DZnhTSHJ6X09tNDQ1Q2pkM2lJMEsxbXN6LW5WbjBOWnBXU2hmc3YzNG5rdDNaLTcwbXlrekM2', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Eramet-JUWI Diogo Off-Grid Solar Project', 'Senegal', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'Eramet, JUWI Renewable Energies', 'announced', 'Eramet and JUWI Renewable Energies have launched what is described as the largest off-grid solar project in Senegal, located at Diogo. The project represents a significant private-sector investment in off-grid renewable energy in West Africa. It is expected to provide reliable solar power to industrial or mining operations in the Diogo area.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2024, NULL, 'https://news.google.', 'https://news.google.', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Senergy 2 Solar Plant Shareholder Reorganisation', 'Senegal', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'Africa REN', 'financing closed', 'Africa REN finalised the shareholder reorganisation of the Senergy 2 solar power plant in Senegal. The restructuring marks a significant change in the ownership structure of the project. This deal reflects continued investor interest in Senegal''s utility-scale solar sector.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2023, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiX0FVX3lxTFBHTDVCYVVsdVdNY0xpX0RpRFgyay1FOGw0RnVqNVZVOGFRa0I5RDgzNnRiVXZTZXl1MzJXcWtORVBwaVgyNkFXdWJ6aDRLdU8xcmotekdwcTQzSTRiM0RN', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiX0FVX3lxTFBHTDVCYVVsdVdNY0xpX0RpRFgyay1FOGw0RnVqNVZVOGFRa0I5RDgzNnRiVXZTZXl1MzJXcWtORVBwaVgyNkFXdWJ6aDRLdU8xcmotekdwcTQzSTRiM0RN', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('AXIAN Energy Solar Investment Senegal (Three Funds)', 'Senegal', 'West Africa', 'Solar', 84, 'AXIAN Energy', 'announced', 'AXIAN Energy is investing $84 million in solar energy projects in Senegal through three dedicated funds. The investment marks a significant commitment by the pan-African energy group to expand renewable energy capacity in Senegal. The deal underscores growing private sector interest in West Africa''s solar energy sector.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2024, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiggFBVV95cUxPX1lWTXdjUEJFTmxqUmoxRXhubWlRTHM5Tnp4QmxESG9vdllBRThLU0MtYXZ6SWlMR0sweDAyY0t6bUp5WnJtQ0lRMG5aWXdhSG40SW4zNEtIaFl6RmhvOU1ERnFGZGc2bGItMTlvZkNwbHNrVWIxNEM2RDNEbjYyNWlR?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiggFBVV95cUxPX1lWTXdjUEJFTmxqUmoxRXhubWlRTHM5Tnp4QmxESG9vdllBRThLU0MtYXZ6SWlMR0sweDAyY0t6bUp5WnJtQ0lRMG5aWXdhSG40SW4zNEtIaFl6RmhvOU1ERnFGZGc2bGItMTlvZkNwbHNrVWIxNEM2RDNEbjYyNWlR?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Kong Solaire Project Côte d''Ivoire', 'Côte d''Ivoire', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'Axian Energy', 'announced', 'Axian Energy is entering the Côte d''Ivoire energy market with the Kong Solaire solar project, marking the company''s first foray into the country. The project represents a key step in Axian Energy''s expansion of its renewable energy portfolio across West Africa. Details on capacity and investment size were not disclosed in the announcement.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMitwFBVV95cUxQMS1RaTBLeXBUVWZaeWtUVkJfaHBjcTIxdlMyZlJ5WUsxX1p3ZWxtbEpMcjNmTjVFZTNWcDdma0tIUVBkdWY2Zk90QnBfOFEycUdpcUpYS3I5OFFTSEx3SUUzV25XdDRxM1VnZWZEb1RBbTZTT2Z1MTZUVjI5eWplaGV6MVl3TTBZYjk3ZzkySWFGc0JMVlFIMmc0T2xqbEpzOHNnaWc2ZzF3bjJLTXlrN0ZBZUlNOXc?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMitwFBVV95cUxQMS1RaTBLeXBUVWZaeWtUVkJfaHBjcTIxdlMyZlJ5WUsxX1p3ZWxtbEpMcjNmTjVFZTNWcDdma0tIUVBkdWY2Zk90QnBfOFEycUdpcUpYS3I5OFFTSEx3SUUzV25XdDRxM1VnZWZEb1RBbTZTT2Z1MTZUVjI5eWplaGV6MVl3TTBZYjk3ZzkySWFGc0JMVlFIMmc0T2xqbEpzOHNnaWc2ZzF3bjJLTXlrN0ZBZUlNOXc?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Bini à Warak Hydropower Project', 'Cameroon', 'Central Africa', 'Hydro', NULL, 'Savannah Energy', 'announced', 'Savannah Energy is seeking to divest a 50% stake in the Bini à Warak hydropower project in Cameroon to attract new investors and co-developers. The partial stake sale is intended to bring in additional capital and partners to advance the project''s development. The move reflects the company''s strategy to de-risk large infrastructure investments in Central Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.?oc=5', 'https://news.google.?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('GDS Orion Solar Plant Ngaoundéré', 'Cameroon', 'Central Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'GDS Orion Solar', 'announced', 'GDS Orion Solar is close to signing an agreement to develop a solar power plant in Ngaoundéré, Cameroon, a project that has been awaited for seven years. The signing would represent a major milestone in bringing utility-scale solar generation to the northern region of Cameroon. No financial details or capacity figures were disclosed in the announcement.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.?oc=5', 'https://news.google.?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Songwe Rare Earth Project DFC Financing', 'Malawi', 'East Africa', 'Grid & Storage', 4.6, 'DFC (US International Development Finance Corporation)', 'financing closed', 'Malawi''s Songwe Rare Earth Project has secured $4.6 million in funding from the US Development Finance Corporation (DFC). The project is focused on rare earth mineral extraction, which is critical to clean energy supply chains including battery storage and electric vehicles. This DFC commitment signals continued US interest in critical minerals investment in Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMilAFBVV95cUxNSHpCQXJBLXRJbWRCQ3ItZG5yamxLaU5wYVoteXZmdVdweU90cnJfdGpVUmlUczVhOG5GMDFWaFhkdkVlTk45SHVrT0ZCTDIyVDFPQUJZSzg2VnRPdEVWUDU2UFNNWm9mYmxWc3BReE4xWFVxdzlJS2NMaDdlckJQR09JWTMwWGJTekt0anEyR1V4OGht?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMilAFBVV95cUxNSHpCQXJBLXRJbWRCQ3ItZG5yamxLaU5wYVoteXZmdVdweU90cnJfdGpVUmlUczVhOG5GMDFWaFhkdkVlTk45SHVrT0ZCTDIyVDFPQUJZSzg2VnRPdEVWUDU2UFNNWm9mYmxWc3BReE4xWFVxdzlJS2NMaDdlckJQR09JWTMwWGJTekt0anEyR1V4OGht?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Rwanda National Solar Electrification Plan 2050', 'Rwanda', 'East Africa', 'Solar', 16000, NULL, 'announced', 'Rwanda has announced a $16 billion solar plan targeting 1,500 MW of new installed solar capacity by 2050, aiming to electrify every home in the country. The plan is part of Rwanda''s broader renewable energy expansion strategy under the Rwanda Energy Group (REG). The initiative represents one of the most ambitious solar programmes in East Africa.', NULL, NULL, 1500, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMisgFBVV95cUxPRjhkSGRkbm5weThVWkVfeHAwUV9vWjVsZHNuM0VVQzhfejBSQVByVTFsNW10a3I2R1FxX0diQmhmbkFFaEVRWWttYzdWUTU3SFdOWGdUUkFqaHN2VzdBajFWZXA1NzFaN1N1YXlOdFcyM3lJSDVySHZUMTI3anF3NkZkSkZGdXlSbEtMWXV4TzhJVHRkLVBIOXpyb215a0Z0UVV0RkYxLW1nMUtKQ1J1RTVB', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMisgFBVV95cUxPRjhkSGRkbm5weThVWkVfeHAwUV9vWjVsZHNuM0VVQzhfejBSQVByVTFsNW10a3I2R1FxX0diQmhmbkFFaEVRWWttYzdWUTU3SFdOWGdUUkFqaHN2VzdBajFWZXA1NzFaN1N1YXlOdFcyM3lJSDVySHZUMTI3anF3NkZkSkZGdXlSbEtMWXV4TzhJVHRkLVBIOXpyb215a0Z0UVV0RkYxLW1nMUtKQ1J1RTVB', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Weranso Solar Power Plant', 'Ethiopia', 'East Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Ethiopia has awarded a contract for the development of the 150 MW Weranso Solar Plant as part of its clean energy expansion programme. The contract award was announced in January 2026 and represents a significant step in Ethiopia''s push to diversify its power generation beyond hydropower. The project is managed under the Ethiopian Electric Power (EEP) framework.', NULL, NULL, 150, 2026, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiugFBVV95cUxQWVpReFVCZHJ3VnZTVTdUa1hYNDRMX2oyRlhVMDVOZFd5SWVpeHhwNndqcTZBVC03ck5sZ0h3a3FXR1dPeGhNVy1FUGdLZkZVekUxXzE0Rmpiclk2dlNjS2RlbEdXbE5ISExtMHVrNVVwWmtZM21RcVFFRzVVaHVSclMycVpnS1hncUljY1c2NC1GcFlrTzVuODRvZGhWajE2Z2JFUFRqbDlQNXl3NzhaT2JTOGRzR1M4Tnc', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiugFBVV95cUxQWVpReFVCZHJ3VnZTVTdUa1hYNDRMX2oyRlhVMDVOZFd5SWVpeHhwNndqcTZBVC03ck5sZ0h3a3FXR1dPeGhNVy1FUGdLZkZVekUxXzE0Rmpiclk2dlNjS2RlbEdXbE5ISExtMHVrNVVwWmtZM21RcVFFRzVVaHVSclMycVpnS1hncUljY1c2NC1GcFlrTzVuODRvZGhWajE2Z2JFUFRqbDlQNXl3NzhaT2JTOGRzR1M4Tnc', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Tanzania 20,000 Solar Home Systems for 120 Islands', 'Tanzania', 'East Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Tanzania launched a programme to deploy 20,000 solar home systems to electrify 120 islands across the country. The initiative is aimed at expanding energy access to off-grid island communities. The project represents a significant step in Tanzania''s rural electrification agenda.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2026, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwwFBVV95cUxOQVA3NUNkbUN3eHlrOVJzaEYyQVU1WHZzbmlkS2ZDbkZlNTdtTGhqTnk3em9ia3JRZVROQTlwU0FBWkt1VkdBREVkRUJrREJ3UmprYXpUZmR0aHM1QTB2SldGMWpXOGl6RHBzU1hmMm54QVowQlFnTm9BeXhXTVdncHN2RjNqR0o3ZUstWXhoNmpaeGFZX0xkVGRhWDJGYXViYzRTa0xKUUxiVkpVX0tJaGVGTk5aZ1Fwa3JPMmUtYkpMTHc', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwwFBVV95cUxOQVA3NUNkbUN3eHlrOVJzaEYyQVU1WHZzbmlkS2ZDbkZlNTdtTGhqTnk3em9ia3JRZVROQTlwU0FBWkt1VkdBREVkRUJrREJ3UmprYXpUZmR0aHM1QTB2SldGMWpXOGl6RHBzU1hmMm54QVowQlFnTm9BeXhXTVdncHN2RjNqR0o3ZUstWXhoNmpaeGFZX0xkVGRhWDJGYXViYzRTa0xKUUxiVkpVX0tJaGVGTk5aZ1Fwa3JPMmUtYkpMTHc', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Kishapu Solar Project Phase One', 'Tanzania', 'East Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'under construction', 'Tanzania''s Kishapu Solar Project has faced fresh delays with Phase One completion now pushed to 2026. The project is a grid-connected solar facility located in the Kishapu district of the Shinyanga region. The delays highlight ongoing execution challenges in Tanzania''s utility-scale solar pipeline.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2026, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwAFBVV95cUxPVkpOUjFFUUJxajZKMkQzaVkwYTVWVGlybjdCc09CSTFsS0dtVWE2ZHplUzRMQ21PWmVxT0o4ZXFPVTNKZWdKSFpld1lPNzJCWlQya0xrTDJEN2NiY3c3RGYxbkhSd2c2WVg3S05zUm1uTG1DM0FLS1dramp0ZzRjVWZRQmJkSHRpaTBmZnBlV2xzeUJqTlVGdXZidUJPelJlQjZQdzJzb0QwVElBM3I4NzFLZ01rM2d6TlYzLXFXSnU', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwAFBVV95cUxPVkpOUjFFUUJxajZKMkQzaVkwYTVWVGlybjdCc09CSTFsS0dtVWE2ZHplUzRMQ21PWmVxT0o4ZXFPVTNKZWdKSFpld1lPNzJCWlQya0xrTDJEN2NiY3c3RGYxbkhSd2c2WVg3S05zUm1uTG1DM0FLS1dramp0ZzRjVWZRQmJkSHRpaTBmZnBlV2xzeUJqTlVGdXZidUJPelJlQjZQdzJzb0QwVElBM3I4NzFLZ01rM2d6TlYzLXFXSnU', true, 'approved', 'Construction', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Zambia Sugar 100 MW Power Generation Expansion', 'Zambia', 'Southern Africa', 'Bioenergy', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Zambia Sugar has announced plans to expand its on-site power generation capacity to 100 MW. The expansion is expected to leverage the company''s existing biomass resources from sugarcane processing operations. The project would significantly increase Zambia Sugar''s self-generation capability and potentially contribute surplus power to the national grid.', NULL, NULL, 100, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiowFBVV95cUxQOVI2X21RT2pFUVhXQ09HVmI5N3QzNlpaV0ZUQUVoXzBmQlNjTTdQOWJ3bDBhaVZFTTZFcURTdWNlb0plZlJVQjFtcjUwOExlZWxRcE5XS2pocTlVTkEzV0FuTzZlTUljbThPOVRzeHRvUVlnUF80M2h6Y1k1SThOeWFPLWNEc3RGLW1WUmF6R3ZmM3BtYmllYTM2ZFR0Nl85MVpB', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiowFBVV95cUxQOVI2X21RT2pFUVhXQ09HVmI5N3QzNlpaV0ZUQUVoXzBmQlNjTTdQOWJ3bDBhaVZFTTZFcURTdWNlb0plZlJVQjFtcjUwOExlZWxRcE5XS2pocTlVTkEzV0FuTzZlTUljbThPOVRzeHRvUVlnUF80M2h6Y1k1SThOeWFPLWNEc3RGLW1WUmF6R3ZmM3BtYmllYTM2ZFR0Nl85MVpB', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Uganda 250 MWh Co-Located Battery Energy Storage System', 'Uganda', 'East Africa', 'Grid & Storage', NULL, 'Energy America', 'announced', 'Uganda''s electricity regulator approved a 250 MWh co-located battery energy storage system (BESS) project led by a subsidiary of Energy America. The project will be co-located with a generation asset to provide grid stability and storage services. This approval marks a significant step in Uganda''s integration of utility-scale battery storage into its power system.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwAFBVV95cUxOMXUzRm5uNU1ScXVSSTFqT0pNQVp5akFEZjNDZ3FwbmIzbTBiTlktQXFzLUJ3Ti05WUlseUFCdFgxVGNWZkczRE9reGlzc0hRcmh4XzFZdFZHcXdIMXd5OVlrZi0zcUlpc2t6V3F5QjNFcTBQb2lKZmcxOEhKSGZRS2Nlalp0WVdxUUVyLWpwOENsclcxcTg2WjJHWGhneldsNGpPT3MwalRObmRhTV9sckU2OGJ1VUEyWko3OHdNWG8', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwAFBVV95cUxOMXUzRm5uNU1ScXVSSTFqT0pNQVp5akFEZjNDZ3FwbmIzbTBiTlktQXFzLUJ3Ti05WUlseUFCdFgxVGNWZkczRE9reGlzc0hRcmh4XzFZdFZHcXdIMXd5OVlrZi0zcUlpc2t6V3F5QjNFcTBQb2lKZmcxOEhKSGZRS2Nlalp0WVdxUUVyLWpwOENsclcxcTg2WjJHWGhneldsNGpPT3MwalRObmRhTV9sckU2OGJ1VUEyWko3OHdNWG8', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Husk Power Rural Solar Mini-Grid Nigeria', 'Nigeria', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'IFC, Government of Canada', 'financing closed', 'The IFC and the Government of Canada have co-invested in Husk Power Systems to catalyze solar-powered economic growth in rural Nigeria. The investment supports Husk''s deployment of solar mini-grids to bring electricity access to off-grid communities. This deal underscores the role of development finance in scaling decentralized clean energy solutions across Sub-Saharan Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMivAFBVV95cUxNVUlWZkVhNldyZXNnbW95cDRTOVJya3VMaldSVUNJNjNDZ2lFQnZjb01TZU02VHRLcm9LUDRxQUgtYk1vYXRuaExLLXZ4RHFtRGFVNVYwT1FPRklSUDQtcFdDQTQ4ZGppVVB5cXlnblgxQ3FvZXFjSDV1TzBqbHFnNWdPWFpxWGYxZkotOGEtOTRwVm96ZUwzMlFyODh3dmJCeGpJRVIydlNydzlQY190WWFLXzRGN0wzYzJTRw', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMivAFBVV95cUxNVUlWZkVhNldyZXNnbW95cDRTOVJya3VMaldSVUNJNjNDZ2lFQnZjb01TZU02VHRLcm9LUDRxQUgtYk1vYXRuaExLLXZ4RHFtRGFVNVYwT1FPRklSUDQtcFdDQTQ4ZGppVVB5cXlnblgxQ3FvZXFjSDV1TzBqbHFnNWdPWFpxWGYxZkotOGEtOTRwVm96ZUwzMlFyODh3dmJCeGpJRVIydlNydzlQY190WWFLXzRGN0wzYzJTRw', true, 'approved', 'Announced', 'Husk Power Systems', 'IFC, Canada', 'IFC', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('AfDB Nigeria Economic Governance and Energy Transition Loan', 'Nigeria', 'West Africa', 'Grid & Storage', 500, 'African Development Bank (AfDB)', 'announced', 'The African Development Bank Group approved a $500 million loan to Nigeria to support economic governance reforms and the country''s energy transition agenda. The facility is designed to strengthen institutional frameworks and accelerate the deployment of clean energy solutions. This is one of the largest single AfDB budget-support operations linked to energy transition in Nigeria.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMi-', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMi-', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Senergy 2 Solar Plant Shareholder Restructuring', 'Senegal', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'Africa REN', 'financing closed', 'Africa REN finalised the shareholder reorganisation of the Senergy 2 solar power plant in Senegal. The restructuring marks a significant corporate milestone for the project''s ownership structure. Africa REN is consolidating its position in Senegal''s solar energy sector through this transaction.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2023, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiX0FVX3lxTFBHTDVCYVVsdVdNY0xpX0RpRFgyay1FOGw0RnVqNVZVOGFRa0I5RDgzNnRiVXZTZXl1MzJXcWtORVBwaVgyNkFXdWJ6aDRLdU8xcmotekdwcTQzSTRiM0RN?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiX0FVX3lxTFBHTDVCYVVsdVdNY0xpX0RpRFgyay1FOGw0RnVqNVZVOGFRa0I5RDgzNnRiVXZTZXl1MzJXcWtORVBwaVgyNkFXdWJ6aDRLdU8xcmotekdwcTQzSTRiM0RN?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('AXIAN Energy Senegal Solar Investment (Three Funds)', 'Senegal', 'West Africa', 'Solar', 84, 'AXIAN Energy', 'announced', 'AXIAN Energy has committed USD 84 million in solar energy investments in Senegal, channelled through three separate funds. The investment underscores AXIAN Energy''s strategic expansion in West African renewable energy markets. The initiative is expected to significantly boost Senegal''s solar generation capacity.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2024, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiggFBVV95cUxPX1lWTXdjUEJFTmxqUmoxRXhubWlRTHM5Tnp4QmxESG9vdllBRThLU0MtYXZ6SWlMR0sweDAyY0t6bUp5WnJtQ0lRMG5aWXdhSG40SW4zNEtIaFl6RmhvOU1ERnFGZGc2bGItMTlvZkNwbHNrVWIxNEM2RDNEbjYyNWlR?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiggFBVV95cUxPX1lWTXdjUEJFTmxqUmoxRXhubWlRTHM5Tnp4QmxESG9vdllBRThLU0MtYXZ6SWlMR0sweDAyY0t6bUp5WnJtQ0lRMG5aWXdhSG40SW4zNEtIaFl6RmhvOU1ERnFGZGc2bGItMTlvZkNwbHNrVWIxNEM2RDNEbjYyNWlR?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Kong Solaire Solar Project', 'Côte d''Ivoire', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'Axian Energy', 'announced', 'Axian Energy is entering the Côte d''Ivoire renewable energy market with the Kong Solaire project, marking the company''s first investment in the country. The project is part of Axian Energy''s broader strategy to expand its solar footprint across West Africa. The announcement was made in October 2025 as part of the continent''s ongoing energy transition.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMitwFBVV95cUxQMS1RaTBLeXBUVWZaeWtUVkJfaHBjcTIxdlMyZlJ5WUsxX1p3ZWxtbEpMcjNmTjVFZTNWcDdma0tIUVBkdWY2Zk90QnBfOFEycUdpcUpYS3I5OFFTSEx3SUUzV25XdDRxM1VnZWZEb1RBbTZTT2Z1MTZUVjI5eWplaGV6MVl3TTBZYjk3ZzkySWFGc0JMVlFIMmc4T2xqbEpzOHNnaWc2ZzF3bjJLTXlrN0ZBZUlNOXc?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMitwFBVV95cUxQMS1RaTBLeXBUVWZaeWtUVkJfaHBjcTIxdlMyZlJ5WUsxX1p3ZWxtbEpMcjNmTjVFZTNWcDdma0tIUVBkdWY2Zk90QnBfOFEycUdpcUpYS3I5OFFTSEx3SUUzV25XdDRxM1VnZWZEb1RBbTZTT2Z1MTZUVjI5eWplaGV6MVl3TTBZYjk3ZzkySWFGc0JMVlFIMmc4T2xqbEpzOHNnaWc2ZzF3bjJLTXlrN0ZBZUlNOXc?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Ngaoundéré Solar Power Plant (GDS Orion Solar)', 'Cameroon', 'Central Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'GDS Orion Solar', 'announced', 'GDS Orion Solar is close to signing an agreement for a solar power plant in Ngaoundéré, Cameroon, a project that has been awaited for seven years. The signing would mark a significant milestone in bringing this long-delayed renewable energy project to fruition. The plant is expected to contribute to improving electricity access in the Ngaoundéré region.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.', 'https://news.google.', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Eco Wave Power Wave Energy Project at Port of Ngqura', 'South Africa', 'Southern Africa', 'Hydro', NULL, 'Eco Wave Power', 'announced', 'Eco Wave Power has completed a feasibility study for a wave energy project at the Port of Ngqura in South Africa, with encouraging results. The study assesses the viability of harnessing wave energy at the port location. This marks an early-stage development milestone for utility-scale wave energy in South Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2026, NULL, 'https://news.google.?oc=5', 'https://news.google.?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Gridworks Independent Transmission Project (ITP) Mozambique', 'Mozambique', 'East Africa', 'Grid & Storage', NULL, 'DFC (US Development Finance Corporation), Gridworks', 'announced', 'The US International Development Finance Corporation (DFC) has provided a grant to Gridworks for an independent transmission project (ITP) in Mozambique. The project aims to develop transmission infrastructure to improve electricity access and grid reliability in the country. This is part of broader US efforts to support energy infrastructure investment across Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiuwFBVV95cUxPelBMY3BtcHN6azlQRkItSzRldmFsaXhlQ0tKQVZqdHd6RXB3aTVEcVhnTDJzRHdCT2RPazJHeDRyYlJFaVdDdUhudkNjTWtzVmxNa0JBckZNZWg3RnFGa0RDdURJQldQbHNGU2c1ejdNZGZmYnFpakhqcEJMZ2EwQVFQQlBOczZxTUJBMy1XREpJY2dLUUIzZHhWMkpKUnd6UWFQVFA1X1VkN01DRldBMW1YdTFfcDdmX3Nv?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiuwFBVV95cUxPelBMY3BtcHN6azlQRkItSzRldmFsaXhlQ0tKQVZqdHd6RXB3aTVEcVhnTDJzRHdCT2RPazJHeDRyYlJFaVdDdUhudkNjTWtzVmxNa0JBckZNZWg3RnFGa0RDdURJQldQbHNGU2c1ejdNZGZmYnFpakhqcEJMZ2EwQVFQQlBOczZxTUJBMy1XREpJY2dLUUIzZHhWMkpKUnd6UWFQVFA1X1VkN01DRldBMW1YdTFfcDdmX3Nv?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Spiro Battery-Swapping Infrastructure Expansion', 'Kenya', 'East Africa', 'Grid & Storage', 50, NULL, 'financing closed', 'Kenya-based electric mobility startup Spiro raised $50 million in funding to meet growing demand for battery-swapping infrastructure across Africa. The investment will support scaling of Spiro''s battery-swap network for electric two- and three-wheelers. The deal signals strong investor confidence in Africa''s e-mobility sector.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2026, NULL, 'https://news.google.', 'https://news.google.', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Ampersand Electric Motorcycle Scale-Up East Africa', 'Kenya', 'East Africa', 'Grid & Storage', NULL, NULL, 'financing closed', 'Ampersand, Africa''s leading electric motorcycle pioneer, secured major investment commitments to scale clean electric transport across East Africa. The funding is intended to expand Ampersand''s fleet and battery-swapping operations in the region. The deal reinforces East Africa''s position as a hub for electric two-wheeler adoption.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.', 'https://news.google.', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Kiira Motors 450-Bus Electric Fleet Deal South Africa', 'South Africa', 'Southern Africa', 'Grid & Storage', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Uganda''s Kiira Motors secured a deal to supply 450 electric buses to South Africa, marking a significant milestone for African-manufactured electric vehicles. The agreement represents one of the largest electric bus procurement deals on the continent. It demonstrates the growing commercial viability of locally produced electric public transport solutions in Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMieEFVX3lxTE5kWE9xVGtYOEhycDNJdE1pYmJ5bjZoSGpTX2lQdGlHX0dwMjkyNlYzN3dfc2tBRnNaUVhHUG5UMmpiRmRJdENPbVdZa2VHZEw0Z0dzTW8yNFVOelRhaU5wTlZhZTN4UjlYV0pMQWw3TkxhZGZlaWVXbA', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMieEFVX3lxTE5kWE9xVGtYOEhycDNJdE1pYmJ5bjZoSGpTX2lQdGlHX0dwMjkyNlYzN3dfc2tBRnNaUVhHUG5UMmpiRmRJdENPbVdZa2VHZEw0Z0dzTW8yNFVOelRhaU5wTlZhZTN4UjlYV0pMQWw3TkxhZGZlaWVXbA', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('EKA Mobility Electric Vehicle Expansion East Africa via Kerchanshe Partnership', 'Ethiopia', 'East Africa', 'Grid & Storage', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Indian EV manufacturer EKA Mobility partnered with Ethiopia''s Kerchanshe Group to expand electric vehicles across East Africa. The partnership aims to introduce EKA''s electric buses and commercial vehicles into the East African market through Kerchanshe''s established distribution network. The deal is part of broader efforts to accelerate EV adoption across the region.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.', 'https://news.google.', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Kenya Adani Energy Deal Cancellation', 'Kenya', 'East Africa', 'Grid & Storage', 2500, 'Adani Group', 'announced', 'Kenya cancelled more than $2.5 billion in energy deals with India''s Adani Group following a US federal indictment against the conglomerate. The cancellation affected multiple energy infrastructure agreements that had been signed with Adani. This represents a significant setback for Kenya''s energy sector investment pipeline.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2024, NULL, 'https://news.google.', 'https://news.google.', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Weranso Solar Plant', 'Ethiopia', 'East Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Ethiopia awarded a contract for the 150 MW Weranso Solar Plant, marking a significant step forward in the country''s clean energy expansion. The contract award reflects Ethiopia''s commitment to scaling up its renewable energy generation capacity. The project is expected to contribute to reducing the country''s reliance on hydro-dominated power generation.', NULL, NULL, 150, 2026, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiugFBVV95cUxQWVpReFVCZHJ3VnZTVTdUa1hYNDRMX2oyRlhVMDVOZFd5SWVpeHhwNndqcTZBVC03ck5sZ0h3a3FXR1dPeGhNVy1FUGdLZkZVekUxXzE0Rmpiclk2dlNjS2RlbEdXbE5ISExtMHVrNVVwWmtZM21RcVFFRzVVaHVSclMycVpnS1hncUljY1c2NC1GcFlrTzVuODRvZGhWajE2Z2JFUFRqbDlQNXl3NzhaT2JTOGRzR1M4Tnc', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiugFBVV95cUxQWVpReFVCZHJ3VnZTVTdUa1hYNDRMX2oyRlhVMDVOZFd5SWVpeHhwNndqcTZBVC03ck5sZ0h3a3FXR1dPeGhNVy1FUGdLZkZVekUxXzE0Rmpiclk2dlNjS2RlbEdXbE5ISExtMHVrNVVwWmtZM21RcVFFRzVVaHVSclMycVpnS1hncUljY1c2NC1GcFlrTzVuODRvZGhWajE2Z2JFUFRqbDlQNXl3NzhaT2JTOGRzR1M4Tnc', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
