    ('Zambia Record PPA Signings for Grid Diversification', 'Zambia', 'Southern Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'announced', 'Zambia has signed a record number of Power Purchase Agreements (PPAs) as the country works to diversify its electricity grid away from hydropower dependency. The PPA signings cover multiple renewable energy projects aimed at reducing Zambia''s vulnerability to drought-related power shortfalls. This marks a significant milestone in Zambia''s energy transition strategy overseen by the Energy Regulation Board (ERB).', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2026, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMitAFBVV95cUxNeVhHbmdHeXJmRnBPY2RZYW1vWG1KUkEtNTBRNzFYeU9DN3dsOVZZNUVTT0JlTUo5Y2U4eHozZDJtS0xUSlpuSWljNlNBLVlyRDBCZllvQ2pzNlBzS2JIZ3p3YjUxX0hNNGY1OUZyMlZSYmlNMDRyWFpTN1FzbkRXVTk4Z3RlS0NsWmF1VUlzMTBiTDhYNFhVc0ZNWDZ6MlVlVjFGeVh1RjY2OFJrQ1IzSm1aSFo?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMitAFBVV95cUxNeVhHbmdHeXJmRnBPY2RZYW1vWG1KUkEtNTBRNzFYeU9DN3dsOVZZNUVTT0JlTUo5Y2U4eHozZDJtS0xUSlpuSWljNlNBLVlyRDBCZllvQ2pzNlBzS2JIZ3p3YjUxX0hNNGY1OUZyMlZSYmlNMDRyWFpTN1FzbkRXVTk4Z3RlS0NsWmF1VUlzMTBiTDhYNFhVc0ZNWDZ6MlVlVjFGeVh1RjY2OFJrQ1IzSm1aSFo?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Zambia 100 MW Solar Plant for First Quantum Minerals', 'Zambia', 'Southern Africa', 'Solar', NULL, NULL, 'operational', 'Zambia launched a 100 MW solar plant supplying power to First Quantum Minerals, a major copper mining operator in the country. The plant represents one of the largest industrial-scale solar installations in Zambia and supports decarbonisation of the mining sector. The project helps address Zambia''s electricity deficit while providing reliable renewable energy to a key industrial consumer.', NULL, NULL, 100, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.?oc=5', 'https://news.google.?oc=5', true, 'approved', 'Commissioned', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('ACWA Power AfDB Sustainable Energy and Water Partnership', 'Egypt', 'North Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'ACWA Power, African Development Bank (AfDB)', 'announced', 'ACWA Power has entered into a partnership with the African Development Bank (AfDB) to boost sustainable energy and water projects across Africa. The partnership was announced in December 2025 and aims to accelerate clean energy infrastructure development. Specific deal size and target countries were not disclosed in the article summary.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiqwFBVV95cUxPNm9taTBUbW82RWZWQVA3R3Zrd1Z5ZDVTOUxLc3dYOVk3ZVBiRVlRekU2ZnlTMGVKaHR6SXNrWU9EUlRCR3laeWpuYjhjVTF2aGxRc3M4ODVRYXRHMVdDMHVEU2Q0OFFPQVRWZVpRTG5zdGxRbmtRbXNJLWhHZThVNFVhVzAyTC1YQVZBUzczWkFXbV9aaWZaRFlXZ2pHVDZfeWg4ejFuenJNTmc', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiqwFBVV95cUxPNm9taTBUbW82RWZWQVA3R3Zrd1Z5ZDVTOUxLc3dYOVk3ZVBiRVlRekU2ZnlTMGVKaHR6SXNrWU9EUlRCR3laeWpuYjhjVTF2aGxRc3M4ODVRYXRHMVdDMHVEU2Q0OFFPQVRWZVpRTG5zdGxRbmtRbXNJLWhHZThVNFVhVzAyTC1YQVZBUzczWkFXbV9aaWZaRFlXZ2pHVDZfeWg4ejFuenJNTmc', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Nigeria AfDB $500 Million Energy Transition Loan', 'Nigeria', 'West Africa', 'Grid & Storage', 500, 'African Development Bank (AfDB)', 'financing closed', 'The African Development Bank Group approved a $500 million loan to Nigeria to support economic governance and energy transition initiatives. The loan is intended to help Nigeria accelerate its shift away from fossil fuels and improve energy sector governance. The announcement was made in November 2025.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMi-', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMi-', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('AfDB $100 Million Loan to EAAIF for Sustainable Infrastructure', 'Nigeria', 'West Africa', 'Grid & Storage', 100, 'African Development Bank (AfDB)', 'financing closed', 'The African Development Bank Group granted a $100 million loan to the Emerging Africa and Asia Infrastructure Fund (EAAIF) to support the development of sustainable infrastructure across Africa and Asia. The loan is intended to mobilise additional private capital for infrastructure projects including energy. The announcement was made in November 2025.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2025, NULL, 'https://news.google.', 'https://news.google.', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Diogo Off-Grid Solar Project (Eramet & JUWI)', 'Senegal', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'Eramet, JUWI Renewable Energies', 'announced', 'Eramet and JUWI Renewable Energies launched Senegal''s largest off-grid solar project at Diogo. The project is designed to power industrial operations in the area and represents a significant milestone in off-grid renewable energy deployment in Senegal. It underscores growing private sector interest in industrial-scale off-grid solar solutions in West Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2024, NULL, 'https://news.google.?oc=5', 'https://news.google.?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
    ('Senergy 2 Solar Plant Shareholder Restructuring (Africa REN)', 'Senegal', 'West Africa', 'Solar', NULL, 'Africa REN', 'financing closed', 'Africa REN finalized the shareholder restructuring of the Senergy 2 solar power plant in Senegal. The reorganization of the ownership structure signals a consolidation of the solar project''s investment base. This transaction reflects ongoing efforts to optimize the capital structure of operational or near-operational solar assets in West Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2023, NULL, 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiX0FVX3lxTFBHTDVCYVVsdVdNY0xpX0RpRFgyay1FOGw0RnVqNVZVOGFRa0I5RDgzNnRiVXZTZXl1MzJXcWtORVBwaVgyNkFXdWJ6aDRLdU8xcmotekdwcTQzSTRiM0RN?oc=5', 'https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiX0FVX3lxTFBHTDVCYVVsdVdNY0xpX0RpRFgyay1FOGw0RnVqNVZVOGFRa0I5RDgzNnRiVXZTZXl1MzJXcWtORVBwaVgyNkFXdWJ6aDRLdU8xcmotekdwcTQzSTRiM0RN?oc=5', true, 'approved', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
